<p class="h1">BELAH*, BELAITE</p>
<p class="fl">KJV rendering of Bela, Benjamin’s oldest son, in <a href="?bref=1Chr.8.1">1 Chronicles 8:1</a>. His descendants were called Belaites (<a href="?bref=Num.26.38-40">Nm 26:38-40</a>; see <span class="sc">nlt</span>). <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=BelaPerson_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Bela (Person) #2</a>.</p>
